	Implement checking for cycle in btree index files.

	* ChangeLog src/gedlib/indiseq.c src/gedlib/init.c
	src/gedlib/names.c src/gedlib/xlat.c
	src/hdrs/list.h src/hdrs/table.h src/interp/interp.c
